,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"120240","content":"没那么漫漫，这点儿东西就一个星期的事儿~","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":"1663285","ctime":1641787758,"ip_address":"","comment_id":329969,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1641704735","product_id":100102601,"comment_content":"当一切都固定下来以后，带来的非但不是限制，反而是自由，<br>很像keep上的一句话：自律给我自由。<br>我喜欢这一切都有章可循的，我更相信老师的说的，场景就是固定那么几种，如果狠心弄，一个星期就可以搞定这些。<br>学到现在，光圈、快门、iOS结合阳光十六法则，锚点参数的基本原理基本上是搞明白了。但是要掌握具体的场景使用相应的锚点参数，并根据情况调整，还需不断实践。<br>路漫漫其修远兮吾将上下而求索！<br>","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1663285,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/61/35/acc2ed75.jpg","nickname":"布步次里-Mai","note":"","ucode":"B1BA13EFFC82A2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":544946,"discussion_content":"没那么漫漫，这点儿东西就一个星期的事儿~","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1641787758,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":329888,"user_name":"Geek_f3e71e","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1794072,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A01231C7FA8A64","user_header":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q3auHgzwzM7ygIXNrAfbEHsmrdjq0JqmWRgpRdKNBu7Zr9j14hQa7rDphqMibEHibykqGmIpN6CuRFOtbGcc3oNg/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1641628199,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"120186","content":"等更新到三十三封以后就不是复习了，就是没在公众号儿发过的新内容了~","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":"1663285","ctime":1641702351,"ip_address":"","comment_id":329888,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"1641628199","product_id":100102601,"comment_content":"上极客再复习一遍","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1663285,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/